      "description": "Sam’s Club. Discover all the perks of being a member with the app. Download today!\n\nSave time and shop easier every day with the Sam’s Club app. Make the most of your membership with easy online shopping for everything from everyday essentials to premium products. With a Sam’s Club Membership you can conveniently shop for fresh groceries, savory snacks, pharmacy prescriptions and more.\n\nHate waiting in line? Thanks to Sam’s Club you can skip the checkout line in the club with convenient Scan & Go™ shopping. Simply shop, scan and pay all in the app. Or schedule your order for Free Curbside Pickup at a time that works for you. Just drive up and get on with your day! While you’re there, save time at the pump. Pay directly in the app for your fuel, at member’s-only prices. Join and see how Sam’s Club makes it easy for you to do more with your day.\n\nSam’s Club also has you covered with prescription management, transfers and refill requests all available in the app. Plus, schedule immunization appointments and more health services. Conveniently get what you need most without having to leave the app.\n\nYour Sam’s Club membership is filled with perks that help you spend less time shopping and more time doing the things you love.\n\nDownload today and get started!\n\n\nSo many benefits!\n\nPremium quality at members-only prices.\n\n· Exclusive Member’s Mark™ brand brings amazing value to help you live your best life.\n\n· Everything you need from home essentials and groceries to snacks and medications.\n\n· Party prep? Cookout celebration? Sam’s Club has you covered.\n\n\nFast & easy ways to shop.\n\n· Skip the checkout line when you shop the club with the Scan & Go™ app feature.\n\n· Get fresh grocery Delivery from Club right to your doorstep. Choose same-day, next-day or fastest Express service to get your order in 3 hours or less. Plus members get free  delivery on eligible $50 orders and have no minimum for $8 for Express*. \n\n· Drive up and let us load your order with Curbside Pickup. Free for all members with no minimum or fees.\n\n· Shop in the app 24/7 and ship products directly to your home.*\n\n\nIn-app Pharmacy.\n\n· Easily transfer prescriptions directly in the app.\n\n· Purchase and refill prescriptions.\n\n· Track prescriptions for the whole family, including your pets.\n\n· Schedule immunizations at your club Pharmacy. Walk-ins also welcome!\n\n\nDownload the app and get the most from your membership today.\n\n*Terms and fees may apply. See SamsClub.com/TermsAndConditions for details.",
